    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/f6555dc74bde5f27a852d0a5f3bd93b7.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>在这个演示版中，你可以探索18个关卡，如果你在所有关卡中都能获得星星，还可以探索更多的附加关卡。<br>有6种可用机制可供在房子的不同区域中旅行，还有许多不同的贴纸。<br>拿上你的贴纸，踏上这段冒险之旅吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/24c1428c27584b9155f182de3621eb99.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br><br>踏上一次史诗般的旅程，穿越你想象中的无限领域，探索散布在你家各处的不同世界。穿过厨房、花园、浴室和许多其他角落，发现新的贴纸，并利用它们的独特力量，揭开这个创意无限、引人入胜的宇宙中的所有隐藏奇迹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/8a5491aa6ffec46616446700e263ac93.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/191387986805c9a09f45a72fee590112.poster.avif?t=1722602019\" width=350 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/191387986805c9a09f45a72fee590112.webm?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/191387986805c9a09f45a72fee590112.mp4?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>如何游戏：从你的笔记本中取出贴纸，并战略性地将它们放置在重力场中。避开障碍物或利用它们的优势，帮助飞船完好无损地到达目的地。每个关卡都有一颗星星，确保获取它以解锁每个世界中的秘密关卡。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/28a48ef958a6ca3205f9bbf575f2e8b8.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=206 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>基于物理学的机制：Stickin’ The Landing 中的重力模拟牛顿物理学，因此作用在飞船上的力与行星的不同质量成正比，与它们之间的距离成反比。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/991e0f97d64e347a1ad3dd5c80739775.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=337 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>无限解决方案：每个关卡都可以通过无限种方式完成，唯一的限制是你的想象力！<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>手工逐帧制作的动画。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>温馨原创的视觉效果。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/b392238ead0a207602c629f9831a6811.webp?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=56 /></span>探索跨越六个不同世界的120多个关卡。发现并体验每个世界提供的独特机制，追求完美的降落！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/293a60417892aa396a68c34f0ceb4721.poster.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/293a60417892aa396a68c34f0ceb4721.webm?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/293a60417892aa396a68c34f0ceb4721.mp4?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/2a7b5548f0785ab8f6a0dd91fa5d0760.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=87 /></span>寻找所有星星，揭开这个世界的隐藏秘密！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/e5ba8a51584753b174cae8a5e434f0c8.poster.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/e5ba8a51584753b174cae8a5e434f0c8.webm?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/e5ba8a51584753b174cae8a5e434f0c8.mp4?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/07a524cd5cfd0a8122277ad2209e2d04.avif?t=1722602019\" width=600 height=75 /></span>每个贴纸都展示出独特的情感，并会根据环境和你的行动动态反应。收集所有贴纸，发现它们的特殊能力！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/1871722f46ca5189ffafaf172481648e.poster.avif?t=1722602019\" width=560 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014590/extras/1871722f46ca5189ffafaf172481648e.webm?t=1722602019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></ul></li></ul></ul></li></ul></ul></li></ul></ul></li></ul></ul></li></ul>",
